# These paths are intentionally different between the `opensource` template
# branch and the private branches (main/dev/preview), and should never be
# silently overwritten by a `git merge dev` (or main/preview) into
# `opensource`: the "opensource" side always wins, and dev's own edits to
# these paths are simply not applied when merging into opensource.
#
# One-time setup required in any clone that will perform that merge
# (this is local git config, not stored in the repo):
#   git config merge.ours.driver true
src/app/about/about-page.tsx merge=ours
public/release.json merge=ours
README.md merge=ours
